NAME
       inode - file inode information

DESCRIPTION
       Each  file  has an inode containing metadata about the file.  An application can retrieve this meta‚Äê
       data using stat(2) (or related calls), which returns a stat structure, or statx(2), which returns  a
       statx structure.

